```
clinical-doppelganger/
├── index.html      ← App shell: 4-tab layout, all HTML containers
├── styles.css      ← All styles: mobile-first, CSS variables, responsive grid
├── icons.js        ← Lucide SVG icon library: ic() and svgIcon() helpers
├── app.js          ← All logic: FHIR, algorithms, statistics, rendering
└── launch.html     ← SMART on FHIR OAuth2 launch entrypoint (6 lines)
```

