        ↓
loadFromFHIR(client)
  ├── Patient.read()
  ├── Condition?_count=50
  ├── MedicationRequest?status=active
  ├── Observation?code=4548-4,55284-4
  └── Encounter?_sort=-date
        ↓
buildFHIRPatient()   ← normalize raw FHIR bundles
        ↓
buildVector()        ← 11-dimensional feature vector
        ↓
cosine(patVec, cohortVec)  ← similarity scores
        ↓
computePSM()         ← propensity score matching
        ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Tab 1: Overview                    │
