## Author Note

This project was built as a graduate-level health informatics course assignment demonstrating:

- SMART on FHIR app integration
- Clinical data modeling with HL7 FHIR R4
- Statistical methods appropriate for observational EHR data
- Explainable clinical decision support design

> The app uses the SMART Health IT sandbox ([launch.smarthealthit.org](https://launch.smarthealthit.org)) for testing with synthetic patient data. No real patient data is used or stored.